-   **Rapid Restoration:** We understand that minimizing system downtime is critical for patient care. Our high-availability servers are designed to restore Electronic Medical Records (EMR/EHR) and imaging archives rapidly.

-   **Local Sovereignty:** All processing occurs securely within our **Seattle (Ballard)** facility, ensuring strict data sovereignty and chain of custody.

**Seattle Data Recovery** empowers healthcare professionals to see their patients with greater clarity. By applying state-of-the-art computational power to medical imaging, we turn data into life-saving insights.

